Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}圣天空战记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要坠入爱河每个人都会变得如此孤单?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正拥抱着比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切必定都是为了让我俩能绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用泪水来呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早就给了我 最宝贵的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是梦?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.57,0:01:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我的幻觉?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在帕拉斯的城楼顶拥抱着的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那晚我见到了我从未见过的亚连的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与那家伙一起飞离了帕拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.06,0:01:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,号码输入完毕后请按下＃字键
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再将话筒挂上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野…学长?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我舍弃了一切前来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍弃了一切?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是国家 战争还是骑士的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都只为了见你一面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,你等很久了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:02:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚…亚连?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使飞舞之日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌,我竟然睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定很累吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续睡没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在喊着"亚连,救救我"说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没死心吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也还真悠哉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才逃过一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且,你还差点就被卖给梅甸了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不是亚连赶过来,我们就逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实生的比较好吃说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,这样也挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的零食
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得其它的怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的唇膏跟我的手表
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得这个味道怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是呼叫器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能吃的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我下来,你这只猫小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气死我了,你这只笨猫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得它们蛮像的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会有那颗石头?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护身符?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我小时候收到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,现在变成了我奶奶的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有其他家人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,爸爸跟妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王 母后是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,我老是跟我弟吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就是爱顶嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过最后挨骂的却总是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"小瞳,你是姊姊啊"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"小瞳,你都已经是高中生了"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"小瞳你是个女孩子耶"之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都听腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸却老是笑笑地在一旁听着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得他们现在过得怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父王与母后在我小时候就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在法尼利亚变成一片焦土
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔卡斯也不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能称的上是我家人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只剩她一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是叫他王兄吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才不是我的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…弗肯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年前,他因为害怕参加王位继承仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕与龙对战而开溜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到他竟然会去投靠寨巴哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且,那家伙居然还想杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,我太激动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会,我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你接下来有什么打算?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过这次的事件,我了解到自己还太过天真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会继续锻炼剑术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切从这里重新开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不能回到亚连的国家去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我现在是寨巴哈军的追捕对象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟我一起来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:07:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,况且说不定还有机会要借助你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会找出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.33,0:08:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你能回到那边去的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备要攻打他国了,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王,请将理由告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:08:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您为何要将亚连关进大牢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个毛头小子不知道会搞出什么花样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要他暂时先安分点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连有做了什么坏事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不光是协助艾斯嘉科尼逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还打算与寨巴哈为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太不像话了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王您才奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会允许那些舰队驻扎我国
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样与其说是同盟国
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是照着寨巴哈的命令在行事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是情非得已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是玛莲妮…那孩子还活着的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莲妮王姊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道寨巴哈打算去攻打弗雷特公国吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既然身为公主那你就该多为国家未来考量才是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情竟然会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚德罗福斯将军下令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源石数量不足
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速采掘及运送作业
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全都不为现场的人着想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来只是一头龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是龙的坟场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的占卜根本就不准嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把我们带来这种危险的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明是占卜安全的方位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的占卜说不定是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要降落了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不能到这种地方来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,我已经得到父王的同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并未听说过有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主,您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概是骨折了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以麻烦你帮我看看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是迦迪斯吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙的坟场是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙在临死前会来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他们又在挖什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们要从龙的化石中采集出能源石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有六架人型装甲是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那采到能源石之后要做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿来作为人型装甲的动力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对,就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你说的能源石是不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼的能源也是来自于能源石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确来说应该是"龙能源石"才对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙能源石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人型装甲还有浮游船的动力都是来自于龙能源石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要像这样从龙的坟场挖出能源石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战场上也是拥有较多龙能源石的人获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两人在这里躲好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让寨巴哈称心如意的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷特?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈要攻打弗雷特公国?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王他打算对西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对他自己的外孙见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在能够阻止这件事的,只有你而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论到哪里,我都会陪着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大还没来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方也差不多要察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长,我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜,我会帮你瞒着父王的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起回城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经下定决心了,王姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟亚连一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要离开这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我放下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主,请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟们,准备起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的,手要动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少给我慢吞吞的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:14:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人型装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守备队快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源石的仓库?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要毁了那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪兰度在追捕的艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个无情的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:16:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是多伦卡喀大人要找的龙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是怎么找到这里的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这男孩真不听话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就来为这位小姐介绍个朋友认识好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被它咬上一□包你马上没命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它很听从我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜,过去打声招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜,送个友谊之吻给她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要真心诚意的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敌人的信号吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,别再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混帐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他的士兵在,快去躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要毁了那座仓库…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他往仓库去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源石产生反应了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源石…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在产生共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,你在哪里?天野
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.21,0:21:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆祝会要开始了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野学长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.65,0:22:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接把你给毁了如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命中注定的相会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽翼的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:56.85,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月儿彼方蓝色探照灯照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.39,0:22:05.30,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降临的天使 你究竟是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:12.93,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的门扉即将开启　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.24,0:22:19.08,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放过这令人兴奋的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:21.44,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:26.45,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃烧般的神秘双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:30.29,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真无邪的笑容让我倾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.36,0:22:34.09,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深处的暗示只传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:38.10,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了无止尽的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:41.60,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心的鼓动无法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:49.07,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想带着你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:56.84,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.39,0:22:05.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:12.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.24,0:22:19.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.14,0:22:21.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:26.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:30.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.35,0:22:34.08,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:38.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:41.60,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:49.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい


